msgstr "保護汝犬免受惡魔侵襲！你可以將其穿在友好的小型四足動物身上，包括狗。"

#: .\items\armor\dog_pets_dog_armor.json
msgid "boiled leather small quadruped barding with caprison"
msgid_plural "boiled leather small quadruped bardings with caprison"
msgstr[0] "帶馬衣的煮制皮革小型四足動物馬鎧"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'boiled leather small quadruped barding with
#. caprison', 'str_pl': 'boiled leather small quadruped bardings with
#. caprison'}
#: .\items\armor\dog_pets_dog_armor.json
msgid ""
"A full barding fofr small quadrupeds including dogs consisting of boiled "
"leather and cloth undercovering. This caparison is depicting a battle "
"between a monstrous dragon and regal griffin. Can be attached to a canine "
"for protection.  You could put this on a friendly small quadruped including "
"a dog."
msgstr ""
"一套為包括狗在內的小型四足動物設計的全套馬鎧，由煮制皮革和布料襯底製成。這件馬衣描繪了兇惡巨龍與威嚴獅鷲之間的戰鬥。可附著於犬類身上提供防護。你可以將其穿戴在友好的小型四足動物（包括狗）身上。"

#: .\items\armor\dog_pets_dog_armor.json
msgid "boiled leather small quadruped barding with bones"
msgid_plural "boiled leather small quadruped bardings with bones"
msgstr[0] "帶骨飾的煮制皮革小型四足動物馬鎧"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'boiled leather small quadruped barding with
#. bones', 'str_pl': 'boiled leather small quadruped bardings with bones'}
#: .\items\armor\dog_pets_dog_armor.json
msgid ""
"Decorative bones affixed to leather small quadruped barding to invoke fear "
"in bandits and raiders and traders all!  You could put this on a friendly "
"small quadruped including a dog."
msgstr "裝飾性骨骼附著於皮革制小型四足動物馬鎧上，用以震懾強盜、掠奪者和商旅！你可以將其穿戴在友好的小型四足動物（包括狗）身上。"

#: .\items\armor\dog_pets_dog_armor.json
msgid "small quadruped rubber rainsuit"
msgid_plural "small quadruped rubber rainsuits"
msgstr[0] "小型四足動物橡膠雨衣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'small quadruped rubber rainsuit'}
#: .\items\armor\dog_pets_dog_armor.json
msgid ""
"A thin plastic covering adapted for small quadrupeds including dogs to "
"protect from acid rain and other caustic sources.  You could put this on a "
"friendly small quadruped including a dog."
msgstr "為包括狗在內的小型四足動物適配的輕薄塑料覆蓋物，用於防護酸雨及其他腐蝕性物質。你可以將其穿戴在友好的小型四足動物（包括狗）身上。"

#: .\items\armor\dog_pets_dog_armor.json
msgid "superalloy tactical small quadruped armor"
msgid_plural "superalloy tactical small quadruped armors"
msgstr[0] "超合金戰術小型四足動物護甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'superalloy tactical small quadruped armor'}
#: .\items\armor\dog_pets_dog_armor.json
msgid ""
"A thin mesh interwoven with superalloy plates and pouches for military "
"working small quadrupeds including dogs that covers from the dewlap to the "
"croup, down to the elbows.  You could put this on a friendly small quadruped"
" including a dog."
msgstr ""
"由超合金板與儲物袋交織而成的輕薄網狀護甲，專為包括狗在內的軍用工作型小型四足動物設計，覆蓋範圍從頸垂到臀部，延伸至肘部。你可以將其穿戴在友好的小型四足動物（包括狗）身上。"

